# Personal MCP tools overlay drop.
#
# Each file is an ES module exporting `{ tools: [...descriptors], handlers:
# { tool_name: async (args) => result } }`. Loaded by `agent/tools-mcp/
# index.mjs` at MCP-server startup and merged into the public tool set.
#
# Anything you place under `_ext/` is gitignored — see .gitignore at repo
# root and docs/architecture-public-private.md.
